data.description: Play GOLF on nearby public golf course less than 1/2 mile away! You'll find yourself close to Seminole CASINO & HOTEL for fun entertainment, JET BLUE Spring Training Center Boston RED SOX entertainment, beautiful SW FL BEACHES, shopping centers, parks, & the convenience of SW FL International Airport. This second-floor 55+ condo offers a convenient lifestyle, with nearly new appliances, including a stove, refrigerator, washer & dryer, and a hot water heater. Step into recently painted interior in neutral colors. The open concept living room and dining room create a spacious atmosphere, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the comfort of tile & carpeted floors throughout, adding to the cozy ambiance of the home. Retreat to the extra-large master bedroom, complete with his & hers closets and a private bathroom. Both balconies were recently fitted with fresh railings and screens, enjoy the cross breeze and natural surroundings. You'll be pleased to know that this condo is steps away from the heated pool. The building features a nearly new roof & the exterior has been recently painted, further enhancing the curb appeal.  This condo is perfect for seasonal or full time living in SW FL.
